## View mode (prefix: z)
Vertically center the line|z / c
Align line to top of screen|t
Align line to bottom of screen|b
Align line to middle of screen (horizontal)|m
Scroll view downwards|j / down
Scroll view upwards|k / up
Move page down|Ctrl-f / PageDown
Move page up|Ctrl-b / PageUp
Move half page down|Ctrl-d
Move half page up|Ctrl-u
